title: Portable RSScrawler 2.0.9.283
description: RSS stands for ?Really Simple Syndication? a common XML standard that allows receiving free news sources such as headlines, breaking news, finance data, weather information or blogs on demand over the Internet. RSScrawler displays your favorite rss news feeds as a flicker-free ticker bar on your Windows Desktop. RSScrawler keeps you always informed in the same way as those ticker bars known from various TV stations.
